description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show JUN-23-2014 MON


The Glenn Beck Program

The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET

        
      
      Big Interviews on the Eve of a Big Election Day 6/23/14

Monday, June 23, 2014 11:04 AM



Facebook: Glenn Beck
Twitter: @glennbeck



Glenn discusses one liberal's kind words about him,
 
    CNN's mocking of Hillary Clinton 

    and what America can do about the border crisis.

    Chris McDaniel joins to talk about his Senate race in Mississippi

    and Dan Bongino discusses his race for Congress in Maryland. 


       That and more on The Glenn Beck Program!
